info:
This is an example flow created by Mac and Huche.
This flow runs once every second because of the Inject "timestamp" node.
The timestamp is fed to the debug node and outputted in milliseconds since 1/1/1970.
Click the debug tab to view these debug messages.
The function node is simple javascript to retrieve the time and date in a specific format.
This formatted date is given to the text dashboard node.
To view this dashboard, click the dashboard tab or go to
http://localhost:1880/ui
